Hi Saima,

To run the demo, you have to have lucene-demos-1.2-rc3.jar and lucene-1.2-rc3.jar in your context classpath. If you're using Tomcat,
you can either have a directory under your application WEB-INF named lib with the jars or put them under Tomcat's common/lib (the
former option is prefered, since probably other applications don't need access to these jars).

Don't forget to configure the demo file configuration.jsp, so that indexLocation points to the place you've created your index.

--Daniel

